accomplished is reminding me how much I miss it.

05:40.050 --> 05:42.310
And--and what is it
you missed, exactly?

05:42.340 --> 05:48.570
****Marmed with nothing but
legal precedent and my wits,

05:48.580 --> 05:50.160
