I'm the one who asks the questions,
eli. That's how this works.

06:07.700 --> 06:09.920
So... your brother?

06:09.930 --> 06:12.210
He's fine. I--
nothing's changed.

06:12.220 --> 06:13.790
You and beth are moving in together?

06:13.800 --> 06:16.880
Well, almost nothing.
Yeah. You cool with it?

