06:40.600 --> 06:43.190
- kind of becoming a parent here.
- yeah.

06:43.200 --> 06:46.560
Well, there'd be pressure,
but dad set the bar pretty low.

06:47.580 --> 06:50.400
- You'll find it, you know.
- What?

06:50.410 --> 06:52.640
Someone to share your life with.

06:53.020 --> 06:55.670
