06:55.980 --> 06:58.340
All right.

06:58.350 --> 07:00.770
All right, then what?

07:05.860 --> 07:08.000
- What are you doing?
- Calling your bluff.

07:08.010 --> 07:10.210
You're signing my permission
slip, just like that?

07:10.220 --> 07:13.660
It's not a permission slip,
and it's not just like that.

07:13.680 --> 07:17.290
We've had three months of sessions,
as you're so fond of pointing out.

07:17.310 --> 07:18.630
