great surprise, I felt invigorated by it.

13:07.130 --> 13:13.600
And I'd been waiting for his return, anticipating
the excitement he brings to this place, but...

13:13.610 --> 13:18.340
but the eli who returned was
more like the man I was engaged to

13:18.350 --> 13:21.590
